{"tid":701577,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"開天窗觀星　扭曲寮仔部規定","createTime":"2018-06-14T08:49:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-14T09:02:52.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cabfb1bc73a7fbb3b6853cb5130f0751a869fe3f","tid":701577,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T08:49:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180614/20420024\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180614%2F20420024&d=CHRw%2BKN%2Fd95I3BdE672PiMP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=c3214e6c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180614%2F20420024&h=c73f232c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180614/20420024</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年06月14日 <br />\n<br />\n開天窗觀星　扭曲寮仔部規定<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180614/large/14la4p04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180614%2Flarge%2F14la4p04.jpg&h=48d1c513&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■鄭先生對記者說，二樓所設的天窗可讓人觀星。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】上世紀五十年代起大陸難民不斷湧入，香港人口急增，住屋供不應求，政府為解決住屋問題，實施寮屋政策。律師鍾卓成解釋：「當時內地有政治運動，跟住又有文革，有好多內地人陸續逃離到新界地方。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n樓市熾熱　寮屋趨商品化<br />\n<br />\n香港人口1945至51年間，由60萬急升至230萬，政府一下子亦難以處理這批新移民。「當年政府喺新界人手不足，好難控制及阻止難民們於山頭野嶺興建房屋，為咗安頓佢哋，政府惟有喺1982年進行了全面嘅寮屋登記，暫緩處理呢一切唔合法嘅建築物，同時控制寮屋數量唔可以再增加。」<br />\n<br />\n地政總署當年設寮屋管制處，專門處理寮屋問題，部門被市民戲稱為「寮仔部」，寮仔部人員會記錄寮屋位置、尺寸、建築物料及用途。並定明不論在政府土地或私人農地上，亦不能違規擴建及搭建新的寮屋。<br />\n<br />\n隨着政府加建公營房屋，全港寮屋由1982年的57萬多間，減至去年的38萬多間，但近年因樓市長處高溫，市民置業有難度，令這批理應自然流失的寮屋群突然「跑出」，漸趨商品化。鍾卓成獲悉鄭先生的豪裝寮屋，不禁批評：「難民時代仲可以有天窗睇星星，起玻璃屋？應該無可能吧。」<br />\n<br />\n■記者黃綺敏  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n違法改裝寮屋呎價$1,100　踢爆平賣農地送豪宅陷阱<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n啟瑞痛罵嘉瑞係「索羅斯」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n違法改裝寮屋　呎價$1,100踢爆平賣農地送豪宅陷阱"},{"pid":"859638a042848561bfcd3a18b62f96c8f0f3bee3","tid":701577,"uid":5477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T08:53:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/14/165257_7410470cb8756b461ccc7e3c07fd6f89.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F14%2F165257_7410470cb8756b461ccc7e3c07fd6f89.png&h=85541f4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb902b5570030db8d73979c48f4db3933d6ee131","tid":701577,"uid":120123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"859638a042848561bfcd3a18b62f96c8f0f3bee3","tid":701577,"uid":5477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T08:53:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/14/165257_7410470cb8756b461ccc7e3c07fd6f89.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F14%2F165257_7410470cb8756b461ccc7e3c07fd6f89.png&h=85541f4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T08:54:09.000Z","msg":"原莎央莉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e39e72ddf063b507a7881cafbc49490f98eff9dd","tid":701577,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T09:02:52.000Z","msg":"1年賺200萬，香港繼續炒地炒樓就得架喇。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}